(0,+\infty)
C^\infty(0,+\infty)
\frac{\partial^2 h}{\partial t^2}(t,x)=\frac{x^2e^{-tx}}{1+x^2}
\left|\frac{\partial h}{\partial t}(t,x)\right|\le\frac{xe^{-ax}}{1+x^2}\in L^1([a,+\infty)),\;\forall a>0
\left|\frac{\partial^2 h}{\partial t^2}(t,x)\right|\le\frac{x^2e^{-ax}}{1+x^2}\in L^1([a,+\infty)),\;\forall a>0
y''(t)=\int_0^\infty\frac{x^2e^{-tx}}{1+x^2}dx
y''
y''(t)=\int_0^\infty\frac{x^2e^{-tx}}{1+x^2}dx=\int_0^\infty\frac{(x^2+1-1)e^{-tx}}{1+x^2}dx=\int_0^\infty{e^{-tx}}dx-y\\=-\frac1te^{-tx}\bigg|_0^\infty-y=\frac1t-y
y''+y=\frac1t
